data.description:
Talk about MOVE IN READY!!! This fantastic home in Medina is the definition of turn key! All furniture and outdoor tools and equipment come with the purchase of this home - making any new home owner's life a breeze! Appreciate living in a neighborhood but having the privacy of a large scenic backyard off of the patio. Many updates throughout the home as well. Do not let this one go unseen! Schedule your showing today! 
Kitchen cabinets, sink, appliances and counter tops were replaced Summer/Fall 2022. HVAC system Fall 2022, Lower 2 levels vinyl/tile plank flooring put in (Summer 2022). Summer 2022 Upper level 3 bedrooms, new paint throughout the home, New RO system for kitchen and refrigerator in 2023, New washer in Dryer 2023, New ADT system 2023
